</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Passenger-side front side-impact sensor has communicated with no response.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1092: Side Impact Sensor Communication Data Invalid (Passenger Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Passenger-side front side-impact sensor has communicated with invalid data.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1095: Side Impact Sensor Communication Data Inconsistent (Passenger Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Passenger-side front side-impact sensor has communicated with inconsistent ID code.
</ptxt>
</entry>
